constructor.details: Constructor of sMATE contract we must pass the following parameters to       initialize the contract and the Evvm contract.

params.AxelarGasService: address of the AxelarGasService contract for the Evvm
params.AxelarGateway: address of the AxelarGateway contract for the Evvm
params.CcipRouter: address of the CcipRouter contract for the Evvm
params.HyperlaneMailbox: address of the HyperlaneMailbox contract for the Evvm
params.LayerZeroEndpoint: address of the LayerZeroEndpoint contract for the Evvm

externalStaking(bool,address,uint256,uin.details: externalStaking allows the users to make a stakingProcess.

params._isStaking: boolean to check if the user is staking or unstaking
params._nonce_Evvm: nonce for the Evvm contract // staking or unstaking
params._priorityFee_Evvm: priority fee for the Evvm contract // staking or unstaking
params._priority_Evvm: priority for the Evvm contract (true for async, false for sync) // staking or unstaking
params._signature_Evvm: signature for the Evvm contract // staking or unstaking
params._user: user address of the user that wants to stake/unstake

goldenStaking(bool,uint256,bytes).details: goldenStaking allows the goldenFisher address to make a stakingProcess.

params._isStaking: boolean to check if the user is staking or unstaking

presaleStake(bool,address,uint256,bytes,.details: presaleStake allows the presale users to make a stakingProcess.

params._isStaking: boolean to check if the user is staking or unstaking
params._nonce_Evvm: nonce for the Evvm contract // staking or unstaking
params._priorityFee_Evvm: priority fee for the Evvm contract
params._priority_Evvm: priority for the Evvm contract (true for async, false for sync)
params._signature_Evvm: signature for the Evvm contract // staking or unstaking
params._user: user address of the user that wants to stake/unstake

goldenStaking(bool,uint256,bytes).notice: only the goldenFisher address can call this function and only         can use sync evvm nonces

presaleStake(bool,address,uint256,bytes,.notice: the presale users can only take 2 SMate tokens, and only one at a time
